<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><a href="/wiki/Coffee_roasting" title="Coffee roasting">Coffee roasting</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Home_roasting_coffee" title="Home roasting coffee">Home roasting coffee</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Corretto_(coffee_roaster)" title="Corretto (coffee roaster)">Corretto</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Decaffeination" title="Decaffeination">Decaffeination</a></div>
